<section class="sb-section sb-section--deep sb-difference" id="SbDifference">
  <details class="sb-mobile-collapse">
    <summary class="sb-mobile-collapse__toggle">
      Why Spellbinder <span class="sb-mobile-collapse__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </summary>
    <div class="sb-container">

    <div class="sb-difference__header">
      <span class="sb-eyebrow">Why Spellbinder</span>
      <h2 class="sb-section-headline">Unlike anything else on the shelf.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="sb-difference__grid">

      <article class="sb-diff-card">
        <div class="sb-diff-card__number">01</div>
        <h3 class="sb-diff-card__title">The Alchemy Advantage — Spagyric Extraction</h3>
        <p class="sb-diff-card__body">An ancient alchemical process that captures the full spectrum of a plant's beneficial compounds — not just isolated fragments. The result: dramatically enhanced bioavailability. The fermentation step also creates beneficial postbiotics that support the gut directly. No other morning beverage brand uses this process.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="sb-diff-card">
        <div class="sb-diff-card__number">02</div>
        <h3 class="sb-diff-card__title">Microbiologist Meets Master Herbalist</h3>
        <p class="sb-diff-card__body">Not a formula assembled by a marketing team. Built by a microbiologist with deep roots in Eastern healing traditions and Western nutritional science — a scientist who asked "what does the body actually need?" and found the answers across two hemispheres of traditional medicine.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="sb-diff-card">
        <div class="sb-diff-card__number">03</div>
        <h3 class="sb-diff-card__title">An Encyclopedia in Every Cup</h3>
        <p class="sb-diff-card__body">Most functional drinks offer 4–6 mushrooms or a single adaptogen. Spellbinder contains over 30 synergistically chosen ingredients — rare teas from six traditions, medicinal fungi, algae superfoods, fermented extracts, TCM longevity botanicals, and warming spices. Each one earns its place.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="sb-diff-card">
        <div class="sb-diff-card__number">04</div>
        <h3 class="sb-diff-card__title">Absolute Purity. Zero Compromise.</h3>
        <p class="sb-diff-card__body">No artificial sweeteners. No seed oils. No gums, binders, or fillers. No vague proprietary blend opacity. Clean ingredients, honestly sourced, transparently shared. Organic and wildcrafted wherever possible. Non-negotiable.</p>
      </article>

    </div>
    </div>
  </details>
</section>

